A cyberpunk scene featuring a sleek handheld device with a display that unfurls like a fabric scroll, glowing with neon cyan and magenta data streams. The device is held by cybernetic hands with chrome fingertips, the flexible screen cascading down like liquid silk. The background shows a rain-soaked futuristic cityscape with holographic billboards reflecting off wet surfaces. The display material has a textile weave texture visible at the edges, transitioning from rigid tech to soft cloth. Dramatic lighting from neon signs illuminates the scene with deep purples and electric blues, steam rising from street vents below.
